profile_positions.description:
• Demonstrated effective leadership and people management skills on FP&A activities, with 
direct supervision of a senior team member;
• Handled Sales and P&L reporting, focusing on financial results and its impacts;
• Held the responsibility of preparing executive materials for the local top board and 
shareholders (Hughes USA & Yahsat UAE), delivering comprehensive financial and business 
reports/analysis to facilitate strategic decision-making;
• Successfully improved OPEX control by coordinating monthly OPEX reports and meetings
with stakeholders, ensuring the EBITDA margin was properly maintained;
• Service Cost report and analysis for B2C departments, utilizing a “volume vs unitary” 
approach aiming to optimize financial performance;
• Led the coordination of the annual Budget process and conducted monthly forecast reviews 
for sales and costs, ensuring alignment with organizational objectives; 
• Maintained regular and collaborative communication with the US Planning department, as
well as local departments, such as Financial, Accounting, Sales, Engineering, and Logistics;
• Skillfully conducted adhoc analysis on Sales, OPEX and CAPEX for the top board, providing 
timely and valuable insights to support strategic decision-making.

• Demonstrated effective leadership and people management skills, coordinating a team of 
two junior members to effectively drive FP&A activities within Brazil's Sales Division;
• Focused on analysing P&L results, as well as conducting sales and margin analysis to optimize 
financial performance;
• Established direct and regular communication channels with Panasonic Group Japan, 
facilitating the creation of monthly Sales and Financial reports to ensure transparent and 
accurate reporting;
• Led monthly P&L Meetings with Panasonic Brazil's Top Board, promoting productive 
discussions on Sales and P&L results for the Sales Division, and collaborating on future 
actions and strategies;
• Successfully coordinated the Annual Budget process and conducted monthly rolling forecast
reviews for Sales and Margin, aligning financial plans with organizational objectives.
• Maintained direct interaction with Japan's financial department and various departments 
within Brazil, including Marketing, Financial, Accounting, Sales, Factory, and Logistics;
• Conducted adhoc analysis on Sales, OPEX and inventory for the top board, providing valuable 
insights to support strategic decision-making and drive business growth.

• Demonstrated effective leadership coordinating FP&A activities for the Broadband B2C and 
Wholesale B2B segments. Responsibilities included conducting comprehensive P&L analysis, 
managing budgets, forecasts, and performing financial adhoc analysis;
• Responsible for preparing executive materials for the Broadband and Wholesale boards, 
providing detailed Financial P&L results and comprehensive financial overviews to facilitate 
decision-making;
• Held a key business leadership role in the annual Capital Approval Committee, successfully 
managing to secure approvals of approximately $5M EUR in 2017 for the Brazil Wholesale 
segment and around $100M EUR in 2018 for the Brazil Broadband segment in collaboration 
with Telecom Italia;
• Initiated the establishment of a new FP&A wholesale department, developing crucial reports 
and routines in collaboration with the Financial, Accounting, Sales, and Engineering 
departments;
• Annual budget coordination and quarterly forecast reviews (Sales, OPEX & CAPEX);
• Efficiently coordinated the annual budget process and conducted quarterly forecast reviews 
for Sales, OPEX, and CAPEX, ensuring alignment with strategic goals and objectives;
• Implemented a monthly analysis routine for OPEX provisions, ensuring accurate financial 
reporting and cost control measures;
• Conducted adhoc P&L analysis for the top board, providing valuable insights and financial 
perspectives to support strategic decision-making.

• Led business analysis initiatives and developed comprehensive budget and forecast revenue 
projections for Fixed Solutions, encompassing broadband and Fixed Telephone services;
• Coordinated the annual budget process and conducted quarterly forecast reviews, ensuring 
alignment of Sales and Revenue goals with strategic objectives;
• Managed multi-departmental tasks for Business Analysis, collaborating closely with 
Marketing, Sales, Network, Finance, and Accounting teams to gather relevant data and 
insights;
• Employed expertise in designing a revenue projection model, resulting in a detailed analysis 
of net revenue at the state and product levels.
